				"description": "Fetches availability of given rooms_ids for a given dates. This API fetches data in bulk, and is essential for ensuring that API Rate Limits does not exceed when we sync all the inventories in our system.\n\n- Expects (number of rooms_ids **x** number of dates) number of items in data.\n    \n- Common Statuses for a slot - CLOSED, AVAILABLE and SOLD_OUT\n    \n- No overlapping or missing slots should be passed at `response.data[x].availability`, should contain data from minutes 0 to minute 1440 _(24hrs \\* 60 min)_"
			},
